gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 129, Mavericks 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Mavericks, 129-113. Domantas Sabonis recorded a season-high 32 points, to go along with 13 rebounds and six assists for the Kings, with DeAaron Fox adding 30 points and seven assists in the victory. Luka Doncic tallied 25 points, 10 rebounds, and seven assists for the Mavericks in the losing effort. The Kings improve to 8-4 in the regular season, while the Mavericks fall to 9-5.
